OL,3,C'Selfish' woman jailed for defrauding
OL,4,Ccharities out of over #150k
OL,6,FA "selfish" woman who defrauded two
OL,7,FBuckinghamshire charities out of more
OL,8,Fthan #155,000 has been jailed.
OL,10,FCharlotte Young, 45, of Griffin Lane,
OL,11,FAylesbury, was sentenced to three
OL,12,Fyears behind bars at Amersham Crown
OL,13,FCourt on Friday (8 May 2026) after
OL,14,Fpleading guilty to two counts of theft
OL,15,Fby employee.
OL,17,FYoung was working as a Treasurer and
OL,18,FAccountant for the Long Crendon
OL,19,FCommunity Social Club and Long Crendon
OL,20,FVillage Association between 2015 and
OL,21,F2023.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
