PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778782268
OL,3,C'Selfish' woman jailed for defrauding
OL,4,Ccharities out of over #150k
OL,6,FDuring that time she took #125,681.92
OL,7,Ffrom the social club's account, and
OL,8,F#29,498.41 from the village
OL,9,Fassociation's account.
OL,11,FShe was arrested on 19 October 2023
OL,12,Fand charged on 21 October 2025.
OL,14,FDetective Constable Stephanie Mason of
OL,15,Fthe Central Fraud Unit, said: "Young
OL,16,Fhad a previous conviction for fraud
OL,17,Fand went on to commit further offences
OL,18,Fin a similar manner, evidently
OL,19,Fbelieving she would evade detection.
OL,26,@wD@_OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
