PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778782268
OL,3,C'Selfish' woman jailed for defrauding
OL,4,Ccharities out of over #150k
OL,6,F"These offences spanned an eight-year
OL,7,Fperiod and had a significant impact on
OL,8,Fa community that had dedicated their
OL,9,Ftime and effort to raising funds for
OL,10,Fcharitable causes.
OL,12,F"The custodial sentence imposed is, in
OL,13,Fmy view, wholly appropriate and serves
OL,14,Fas a clear reminder that such actions
OL,15,Fcarry serious consequences."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
