PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778782268
OL,3,C'Selfish' woman jailed for defrauding
OL,4,Ccharities out of over #150k
OL,6,FCentral Fraud Unit Detective Inspector
OL,7,FDuncan Wynn said: "I am pleased with
OL,8,Fthis conviction which comes after
OL,9,FYoung pleaded guilty following a
OL,10,Fthorough and extensive investigation
OL,11,Fby DC Stephanie Mason and the
OL,12,FBuckinghamshire Fraud Team.
OL,14,F"The sentence reflects the severity of
OL,15,Fthe offences whereby Young
OL,16,Fsystematically exploited the position
OL,17,Fof trust she was placed into and stole
OL,18,Fover #150,000 of money which was
OL,19,Fraised by the community for charitable
OL,20,Fpurposes.
OL,26,@oD@SOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
