PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778782268
OL,3,C'Selfish' woman jailed for defrauding
OL,4,Ccharities out of over #150k
OL,6,F"These selfish acts have left a huge
OL,7,Fwhole in much needed community funds.
OL,8,FYoung showed complete disregard for
OL,9,Fthis and covered her tracks well
OL,10,Fenough to be able to live a lavish
OL,11,Flifestyle on these ill-gotten gains
OL,12,Ffor 8 years.
OL,14,F"I hope that the sentence imposed will
OL,15,Fact as a deterrent to others and
OL,16,Fdemonstrate our commitment to pursue
OL,17,Ffraudsters and bring them to justice
OL,18,Fon behalf of victims.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
