OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778782268
OL,3,C'Selfish' woman jailed for defrauding
OL,4,Ccharities out of over #150k
OL,6,F"Thames Valley Police will use all
OL,7,Fproceeds of crime powers available to
OL,8,Fensure as much of the stolen money as
OL,9,Fpossible can be returned to the victim
OL,10,Fand will ensure Young is stripped of
OL,11,Fany assets and financial benefit she
OL,12,Facquired using stolen funds."
